trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support in a visual designer for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton"></xref> Web server control.
trans-unit.target: Gir støtte for utforming i en visuelle utformeren for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton"> </xref> Web serverkontroll.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> control implements the functionality of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink> control with the visual appearance of a button.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton>kontrollen implementerer funksjonaliteten til en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink>kontroll med utseendet til en knapp.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HyperLink> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton>

trans-unit.source: In a visual designer, when you switch from Source to Design view, the markup source code that describes a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> control is parsed and a design-time version of the control is created on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: I en visuelle utformeren når du bytter fra kilden til utformingsvisning markup kildekode som beskriver en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton>kontrollen analyseres og en utformingen versjon av kontrollen er opprettet på utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton>

trans-unit.source: When you switch back to Source view, the design-time control is persisted to the markup source code and edited into the markup for the Web page.
trans-unit.target: Når du går tilbake til visning i datakilden, er utformingen kontrollen beholdt i markup kildekode og redigeres i markup for websiden.

trans-unit.source: The LinkButtonDesigner class provides design-time support for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> control.
trans-unit.target: Klassen LinkButtonDesigner gir støtte for utforming for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LinkButtonDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LinkButtonDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The .NET Framework internally constructs a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LinkButtonDesigner> class when it creates the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> control or a copy of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: .NET Framework internt bygger en ny forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LinkButtonDesigner>klasse når det oppretter den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton>kontroll eller en kopi av det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton>kontrollen i utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.LinkButtonDesigner>
